title: 3 and Out - NFL Week 1 Reaction
itunes:title: 3 and Out - NFL Week 1 Reaction
description:
John reacts to a NFL Week 1, including Tom Brady leading the Bucs to a convincing win over the Cowboys despite off-field distractions, Lamar Jackson’s decision to play without a long term deal. He also buys or sells his week 1 takes.
